<title>USA: Sterling Commerce Inc names CFO.</title>
<headline>Sterling Commerce Inc names CFO.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS, Texas 1997-01-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sterling Commerce Inc said Monday it had named Steven Shiflet chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Shiflet succeeds Jeannette Meier, who is to continue with the company as executive vice president, general counsel and secretary.</p>
<p>Shiflet previously was group vice president of finance and administration of the electronic commerce group of its unit, Sterling Software, the company said.</p>
<p>Sterling Commerce provides electronic software products and services.</p>
